#. Plugin Name of the plugin/theme
msgid "Simple Footnotes"
msgstr "Notes de bas de page simples"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin/theme
msgid "https://github.com/mcaskill/wp-simple-footnotes"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"Create simple, elegant footnotes on your site. Use the <code>[ref note=\"My "
"note.\" /]</code> shortcode (<code>[ref note=\"My note.\"]My marker.[/ref]</"
"code>) and the plugin takes care of the rest. There's also a <a href="
"\"options-reading.php\">setting</a> that enables you to move the footnotes "
"below your page links, for those who paginate posts."
msgstr ""
"Créez des notes de bas de page simples et élégantes sur votre site. Utilisez "
"<code>[ref note=\"My note.\" /]</code> le shortcode ( <code>[ref note=\"My "
"note.\"]My marker.[/ref]</code> ) et le plugin prend soin du reste. Il "
"existe également un paramètre <a href=\"options-reading.php\">qui vous</a> "
"permet de déplacer les notes de bas de page sous les liens de votre page, "
"pour ceux qui paginent les publications."

#. Author of the plugin/theme
msgid "Chauncey McAskill, Andrew Nacin"
msgstr ""
